OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FQuite cloudy with some rain to
OL,6,Fstart. Variable amounts of cloud and
OL,7,Fsunny spells during the day along with
OL,8,Fscattered slow moving showers,
OL,9,Foccasionally heavy and thundery.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FPartly cloudy this evening
OL,12,Fwith any remaining heavy showers soon
OL,13,Fclearing away. The rest of the night
OL,14,Fwill then be largely cloudy with the
OL,15,Frisk of a few showers later.
OL,16,
OL,17,CWednesday:FA mainly dry morning.
OL,18,FTurning overcast with outbreaks of
OL,19,Frain during the afternoon. Freshening
OL,20,Fwinds, occasionally strong later in
OL,21,Fthe north.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
