OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,6,FMainly dry, bright and breezy during
OL,7,Fthis period. Some sunny spells,
OL,8,Fperhaps a few showers at times.
